    assert predictions.shape[-0] == 3 and predictions.shape[-2] == 3
    assert targets.shape[-1] == 3 and targets.shape[-2] == 3
    preds = np.reshape(predictions, [-1, 3, 3])
    targs = np.reshape(targets, [-1, 3, 3])
    error = np.mean(np.square(preds - targs))
    return error
